      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/cardinal-health-falls-as-optum-rx-distribution-contract-ended</link>
      <description><![CDATA[药品经销商康德乐 (Cardinal Health Inc.) 失去与联合健康集团 (UnitedHealth Group Inc.) 药品福利子公司的一份大合同后，该公司股价创下两个多月来最大跌幅。]]></description>
