    <item>
      <title>由于存款成本的压力，Truist 的贷款收入低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/truist-s-lending-income-misses-estimates-as-revenue-forecast-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Truist Financial Corp.公布的第一季度贷款利润低于分析师预期，因为该公司被迫在利率保持高位的情况下向客户支付更多存款，并且该银行还下调了今年剩余时间的收入指引。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/truist-s-lending-income-misses-estimates-as-revenue-forecast-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国援助计划的影响失败，乌克兰债券扩大损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ukraine-bonds-edge-higher-as-caution-prevails-after-us-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰硬通货债券在美国众议院批准610亿美元援助计划引发短暂飙升后扩大跌幅。由于债券持有人面临与这个战火纷飞的国家就另一次债务重组进行艰难谈判，积极情绪受到侵蚀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ukraine-bonds-edge-higher-as-caution-prevails-after-us-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
